### Deve retornar 200 sem token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/eventos

### Deve retornar 403 sem token (POST agora exige auth)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json

{ "eventName": "Teste sem auth" }

### Deve retornar 201 com token admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "eventName": "Data Engineering Day",
  "capacity": 100,
  "isFree": true,
  "scheduledAt": "2026-10-10T20:00:00",
  "price": 0.0,
  "expectedAttendance": 80,
  "isWeekend": false,
  "category": "CORPORATIVO",
  "creatorId": 3
}

### Adicionar usuário como admin de um evento
### (insere uma linha na tabela event_admins)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos/5/admins/3
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}